                         Encoder/Ripper: SMiLE                         
                                                                        
   Whole reason for the READNFO is just to say that this is a 3D CAM,   
   but it's only really the first minute where the 3D is really         
   noticeable, but there are the odd moments when the video does        
   wobble. Not the best but it is watchable. For starters we took the   
   source and dropped it into conversion, then we ran a few filters     
   over it before then running our custom encode settings on it. We     
   went for a lower res as we think that it's better for this video.    
   The audio is pretty good for a CAM, video can also get dark in       
   places, but it's pretty good for a first CAM. Remember that it's     
   free and enjoy! 
